WEBVTT

00:00:15.549 --> 00:00:19.577
iz nokh di milkhome, vi ayer lebn hot zikh tsuzamen,

00:00:20.679 --> 00:00:22.293
hot zikh bakumen...?

00:00:23.075 --> 00:00:29.026
n- ikh hob nit gearbet di gantse tsayt un... ikh hob gearbet mit ⟨Bunemen⟩ tsuzamen

00:00:29.319 --> 00:00:31.063
hob ikh gearbet.

00:00:31.849 --> 00:00:36.886
az okh un az vey vos ikh hob fardint, nor, ikh veys? tsu dershtukeven.

00:00:36.949 --> 00:00:41.143
az s'iz shoyn geborn gevorn a kind, iz shoyn gevezn shver.

00:00:44.490 --> 00:00:46.273
di yidishe

00:00:47.662 --> 00:00:51.622
bafelkerung in Vilne, efsher gedenkt ir?

00:00:52.927 --> 00:00:57.511
efsher hot ir zikh getrofn mit ayere bakante fun geto?

00:00:57.990 --> 00:00:59.088
fun geto?

00:00:59.088 --> 00:01:02.489
nu, di vos zaynen geforn mit mir iz

00:01:03.626 --> 00:01:07.977
hob ikh getrofn, nor di nemen, di familye, farshteyt ir,

00:01:07.977 --> 00:01:10.725
mir zaynen dokh nit ale geven tsuzamen.

00:01:15.658 --> 00:01:17.576
efsher gedenkt ir dem

00:01:17.683 --> 00:01:21.677
dem yidishn lebn in Vilne nokh di milkhome.

00:01:23.825 --> 00:01:28.426
m'hot gehorevet, veyst ir dokh. mayn man hot gehorevet

00:01:28.483 --> 00:01:31.380
hot zikh gevelt aroyfarbetn a bisl.

00:01:31.554 --> 00:01:34.833
undzer, undzer kvatir hot ir dokh gezen.

00:01:34.833 --> 00:01:36.900
eyn tsimerl hobn mir gehat.

00:01:37.528 --> 00:01:39.092
vu hot ir gelebt?

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:41.758
un m'hot gehorevet un m'hot ah mir hobn gelebt oyf

00:01:42.341 --> 00:01:45.791
tsum ban, vi ruft zikh on di dire dortn?

00:01:46.758 --> 00:01:48.018
di gas?

00:01:49.425 --> 00:01:50.415
SODU.

00:01:50.505 --> 00:01:51.633
Sode-gas.

00:01:51.669 --> 00:01:52.372
DA.

00:01:53.812 --> 00:01:54.667
Sode.

00:01:57.137 --> 00:02:04.455
nu, un m'hot ge- geven, m'hot gehorevet, gezukht arbet un me zol kenen zikh a bisl tsu-UNK.

00:02:05.304 --> 00:02:07.222
un dos hot undz oykh gekost.

00:02:09.371 --> 00:02:11.829
di shul in Vilne,

00:02:12.864 --> 00:02:16.115
a shul in Vilne iz geven nokh di milkhome?

00:02:15.830 --> 00:02:18.225
far vos nit? s'iz geven.

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:21.313
geven ot o do.

00:02:23.597 --> 00:02:29.059
ir flegt dertseyln eynem dem tsveytn, ir flegt zikh trefn mit mentshn, mit

00:02:29.233 --> 00:02:30.527
khaveyrim?

00:02:30.228 --> 00:02:33.609
ye, mir flegn ale dray un tsvantsik yore-

00:02:34.937 --> 00:02:36.214
YANVAR'

00:02:36.523 --> 00:02:40.241
flegn mir zikh tsuzamentrefn, mir flegn makhn a

00:02:40.252 --> 00:02:41.461
ovnt-broyt.

00:02:42.497 --> 00:02:44.348
dos iz geven der tog?

00:02:45.703 --> 00:02:47.756
velkher tog iz dos geven?

00:02:47.880 --> 00:02:52.026
dos iz, ven s'iz oysgefaln der dray un tsvantsikster YANVAR'.

00:02:51.862 --> 00:02:53.105
ven men aykh

00:02:52.655 --> 00:02:54.422
flegn mir makhn a VECHER,

00:02:54.815 --> 00:02:58.508
ven men flegt aykh ba- ven men hot aykh bafrayt?

00:02:57.524 --> 00:02:59.134
bafrayt, ye.

00:02:59.642 --> 00:03:04.682
iz dan flegt men makhn a VECHER un me flegt dermonen

00:03:04.957 --> 00:03:10.807
dem lebn fun, fun geto, fun di l-, fun lager, flegt men dos dermonen.

00:03:11.910 --> 00:03:15.330
ver flegt kumen oyf ot o di ovntn?

00:03:16.061 --> 00:03:22.097
nu, di noentste, iz gevezn, di Pesye Brener iz gevezn,

00:03:22.575 --> 00:03:26.445
s'iz geven Khane Grinberg, s'iz geven,

00:03:26.456 --> 00:03:28.897
der, vi ⟨hot er⟩ geheysn

00:03:29.156 --> 00:03:30.754
der shnayder

00:03:31.704 --> 00:03:33.572
s'iz geven a fule.

00:03:33.662 --> 00:03:35.462
Simke Dvorets

00:03:36.193 --> 00:03:37.402
iz geven.

00:03:40.479 --> 00:03:42.751
Feygele Kaltenovski

00:03:44.445 --> 00:03:46.954
⟨fleg⟩ zayn, me flegt zikh tsuzamenklaybn.

00:03:52.764 --> 00:03:54.615
Khasye Gravets.

00:03:54.907 --> 00:03:57.449
zi iz shoyn nito, shoyn geshtorbn.

00:04:02.889 --> 00:04:06.393
Hodke, di familye hob ikh nit gevust, iz gevezn.

00:04:12.913 --> 00:04:15.947
ir gedenkt vos flegt ir dertseyln eynem

00:04:15.947 --> 00:04:17.648
eyner dem tsveytn?

00:04:18.127 --> 00:04:22.205
ot dos vos mir hobn iberlebt hobn mir dertseylt.

00:04:23.595 --> 00:04:25.344
zitsn, dertseyln.

00:04:25.890 --> 00:04:29.006
s'iz geven, s'hot geklekt fun di rusn oykh.

00:04:29.585 --> 00:04:34.439
flegn araynkumen bay nakht un zey flegn veln me zol geyn mit zey.

00:04:35.087 --> 00:04:36.501
un mir zogn "neyn.

00:04:36.501 --> 00:04:38.793
oybe geyn, veln mir geyn ale.

00:04:39.272 --> 00:04:41.640
keyn eyntsike UNK lozn mir nit."

00:04:41.640 --> 00:04:42.186
⟨neyn⟩.

00:04:42.647 --> 00:04:44.700
s'hot geklekt fun zey, ye.

00:04:52.265 --> 00:04:56.377
efsher ayere khaveyrim flegn aykh vos nit iz dertseyln

00:04:57.075 --> 00:04:59.145
vegn di iberlebenish.

00:04:59.310 --> 00:05:00.224
vegn vos?

00:05:00.095 --> 00:05:02.486
vegn dos vos zey hobn ibergelebt.

00:05:03.588 --> 00:05:08.116
nu vos hobn zey gekent dertseyln? dos vos ikh hob gezen, efsher hobn zey gehat

00:05:08.116 --> 00:05:09.000
merer.

00:05:14.928 --> 00:05:17.420
vi hot gevaksn ayer zun?

00:05:18.337 --> 00:05:19.361
mayn zun?

00:05:19.468 --> 00:05:21.302
vi hot er gevaksn?

00:05:21.948 --> 00:05:25.123
nu, lernen zeyer hot er nit gevelt.

00:05:25.205 --> 00:05:27.793
nor vos, arbetn hot er gevelt.

00:05:27.793 --> 00:05:29.266
arbetn vil er.

00:05:30.690 --> 00:05:32.001
nu, gornit.

00:05:32.816 --> 00:05:36.620
azoy ⟨az⟩ halt er zikh fayn, er firt zikh oyf zeyer fayn.

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:40.011
dem zun flegt ir dertseyln?

00:05:40.011 --> 00:05:43.678
er hot gevust vos ir hot ibergelebt mitn man?

00:05:43.852 --> 00:05:46.141
nu, far vos zol er nit visn?

00:05:46.637 --> 00:05:51.053
er flegt leyenen, s'iz geven bikher, flegt er leyenen andersh mol

00:05:51.902 --> 00:05:53.314
fun di geto.

00:05:58.770 --> 00:06:02.528
yidishe yontoyvim flegt ir fayern in shtub?

00:06:02.921 --> 00:06:03.742
mir?

00:06:03.512 --> 00:06:04.401
ye.

00:06:04.642 --> 00:06:08.349
nu, me flegt makhn yontev, yomkiper

00:06:08.827 --> 00:06:10.656
flegt men haltn

00:06:10.667 --> 00:06:12.450
sukes

00:06:12.827 --> 00:06:14.425
rosheshone me falt-

00:06:14.514 --> 00:06:16.114
flegt haltn dem

00:06:16.114 --> 00:06:16.888
dem...

00:06:17.417 --> 00:06:18.323
in shtub.

00:06:18.598 --> 00:06:22.001
vi flegt ir dos in shtub haltn di yontoyvim?

00:06:22.023 --> 00:06:23.131
vos vifl?

00:06:22.901 --> 00:06:24.887
vi, vi flegt ir?

00:06:25.652 --> 00:06:28.161
vifl s'flegt oyskum-, peysekh.

00:06:30.431 --> 00:06:32.370
ober dem...

00:06:30.562 --> 00:06:33.155
vos flegt zayn oyf peysekh bay aykh?

00:06:33.312 --> 00:06:34.050
ah?

00:06:33.802 --> 00:06:36.479
vos flegt zayn bay aykh oyf peysekh?

00:06:36.671 --> 00:06:38.589
nu, matse

00:06:38.831 --> 00:06:41.478
veyst ir dokh, mistome flegt dokh gebn...

00:06:41.478 --> 00:06:44.411
andersh mol git dokh di yidishe obtshestve

00:06:44.501 --> 00:06:45.845
tsu farzukhn.

00:06:50.441 --> 00:06:53.543
shoyn, mayn zun iz gekumen. shoyn geendikt tsi nit?

00:06:53.546 --> 00:06:55.785
ikh hob nokh mit im vos tsu reydn.

00:06:56.533 --> 00:07:05.167
dernokh, vi vi hot zikh bay aykh, vi der zun hot ge- zayn lebn, vi bay im hot zikh alts bakumen in lebn?

00:07:05.207 --> 00:07:06.180
lebn fayn.

00:07:06.570 --> 00:07:08.121
fay- zey lebn fayn.

00:07:08.514 --> 00:07:09.875
fayn, me

00:07:10.370 --> 00:07:12.643
keyn iberreyd iz nito bay zey.

00:07:12.817 --> 00:07:16.687
vos zi vil, vos zi vil, dos tut zi. i er dos glaykh.

00:07:16.687 --> 00:07:18.482
zi iz d-, zi iz zeyer a gute.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:20.790
zeyer a gute iz zi.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:22.802
ir hot eyniklekh?

00:07:23.111 --> 00:07:24.146
eyniklekh?

00:07:24.157 --> 00:07:28.151
nu, der eynikl vos iz do in ISRAEL, mer hob ikh nit.

00:07:30.367 --> 00:07:33.601
er veys vegn dos vos ir hot ibergelebt?

00:07:33.303 --> 00:07:35.761
nu, dos vos ikh hob aykh dertseylt

00:07:36.408 --> 00:07:38.664
un er hot gezesn oykh un farshribn.

00:07:40.374 --> 00:07:43.490
⟨nor⟩ kh'hob ongehoybn veynen, zogt er "SHO SHO NE NADO".

00:07:47.462 --> 00:07:49.886
dos iz nokh an ol, mayn tayere.

00:07:51.242 --> 00:07:54.614
⟨me hot⟩ undz a mol aroysgefirt oyf a feld grobn

00:07:54.617 --> 00:07:55.778
naket

00:07:55.781 --> 00:07:57.423
i- un osyen.

00:07:57.423 --> 00:07:59.099
regn, kalt.

00:07:59.780 --> 00:08:02.744
hobn mir gezogt tsum postn "shis undz avek."

00:08:02.987 --> 00:08:05.361
zogt er, er hot nit keyn PRAV

00:08:06.412 --> 00:08:08.089
tsu shisn undz.

00:08:08.117 --> 00:08:09.360
keyn bafel.

00:08:10.901 --> 00:08:14.372
nu, mir zaynen gekumen mit zi zelbe ⟨hetsoes⟩ tsurik.

00:08:15.187 --> 00:08:22.454
dos iz strashne geven. dos, de- mer nit gedarft zen vi dos iz forgekumen alts. ⟨az⟩ reydn iz gornit.

00:08:24.097 --> 00:08:27.078
ir flegt zikh eyne di tsveyte helfn

00:08:27.860 --> 00:08:29.626
in ot azane faln?

00:08:30.476 --> 00:08:31.500
helfn?

00:08:31.202 --> 00:08:33.660
ye, eyne di tsveyte.

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:32.660
mit

00:08:33.209 --> 00:08:34.942
un mit vos hot men gekent helfn?

00:08:35.808 --> 00:08:39.700
nu, mit a gutn vort, mit a lid, mit a

00:08:39.808 --> 00:08:42.232
mir hobn gornit gehoft az mir veln blaybn lebn.

00:08:43.419 --> 00:08:44.628
nit gehoft.

00:08:46.102 --> 00:08:46.800
az mir

00:08:46.800 --> 00:08:49.080
s'iz dokh zeyer fil oysgefaln.

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:52.678
bay undz iz nor geven nishkoshe, nor bay di mener

00:08:53.814 --> 00:08:55.766
ale tog flegt men bagrobn.

00:08:56.784 --> 00:08:59.599
zey hobn nit gekent aribertrogn. zey hobn gehat

00:08:59.599 --> 00:09:01.790
shreklekhe shvere arbet.

00:09:01.982 --> 00:09:05.633
vos zey flegn darfn trogn oyf zikh

00:09:05.633 --> 00:09:09.300
di ts- zeklekh tsement, shtelt zikh for.

00:09:09.744 --> 00:09:15.425
hobn zey dos nit gekent oyshaltn. hungerik, naket, borves, balayzikt.

00:09:15.853 --> 00:09:19.324
un zey hobn dos nit gekent aribertrogn, vos zey hobn gemuzt.

00:09:20.477 --> 00:09:22.463
zey hobn gefaln, zaynen gefaln.

00:09:23.430 --> 00:09:26.816
ir hot dos gezen, tsu ir hot nor gehert vegn dem?

00:09:25.770 --> 00:09:27.541
er flegt dos dertseyln.

00:09:27.615 --> 00:09:28.571
mayn man.

00:09:28.357 --> 00:09:29.414
ayer man.

00:09:28.965 --> 00:09:29.955
ye.

00:09:32.036 --> 00:09:34.612
di shtub gegesn di layz.

00:09:34.787 --> 00:09:36.688
di gnides oyfgegesn

00:09:37.588 --> 00:09:39.894
s'hot zey oyfgegesn. nu, hungerik...

00:09:41.486 --> 00:09:43.272
nu, shoyn? shoyn geendikt?

00:09:43.292 --> 00:09:44.943
s'iz shoyn geendikt di

00:09:44.962 --> 00:09:46.273
di plyonke oykh.

00:09:46.312 --> 00:09:48.264
s'iz nokh nit geendikt.

00:09:47.426 --> 00:09:48.141
neyn!

00:09:48.141 --> 00:09:48.723
neyn.

00:09:48.723 --> 00:09:52.078
mer far alem, git tsu mir vos ikh veys keyn zakh nit.

00:09:52.809 --> 00:09:56.249
ir veyst zeyer gut, ir dertseylt zeyer gut.

00:09:55.529 --> 00:09:56.149
ha?

00:09:56.249 --> 00:09:58.473
ir dertseylt zeyer gut.

00:09:58.968 --> 00:10:03.438
ir treyst mir. ir muzt mir a bisl azoy oyfheybn.

00:10:00.133 --> 00:10:01.359
ye.

00:10:03.438 --> 00:10:05.139
az ikh zol hobn kheyshek.

00:10:07.237 --> 00:10:08.716
un

00:10:08.096 --> 00:10:11.586
vifl krigt ir a monat far aza min arbet?

00:10:12.620 --> 00:10:18.858
un, ir gedenkt efsher velkhe nit iz lider flegt men bay aykh zingen?

00:10:19.100 --> 00:10:20.512
yidishe?

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:22.132
me flegt ye zingen di geto-lider.

00:10:22.577 --> 00:10:25.693
velkhe geto-lider gedenkt ir?

00:10:27.150 --> 00:10:28.747
me flegt zingen

00:10:31.841 --> 00:10:34.299
me flegt zingen zeyer fayne lider, ober

00:10:34.676 --> 00:10:35.598
ikh gedenk nit.

00:10:36.414 --> 00:10:37.939
zeyer fayne ge-

00:10:37.939 --> 00:10:39.463
aleyn

00:10:39.722 --> 00:10:41.370
tsuzamengeshtelt

00:10:41.527 --> 00:10:42.483
aleyn.

00:10:44.193 --> 00:10:47.084
vu hot ir zey gehert dem ershtn mol di lider

00:10:47.084 --> 00:10:49.233
di tsuzamengeshtelte?

00:10:48.270 --> 00:10:50.100
me flegt in geto,

00:10:50.100 --> 00:10:52.949
s'iz rekht az in geto flegt men zikh trefn

00:10:52.949 --> 00:10:54.181
in a shtub

00:10:54.183 --> 00:10:58.146
un me flegt oykhet, s'iz do mentshn vos zaynen gegangen

00:10:58.146 --> 00:11:00.272
un oysgebitn di zakhn

00:11:00.292 --> 00:11:01.586
vos zey hobn gehat,

00:11:02.081 --> 00:11:03.892
zey hobn nit gezhalevet.

00:11:03.937 --> 00:11:11.613
un far derayn flegn zey krign esn. gelt iz nit, gelt hobn mir nit gedarft di gelt, vayl mir hobn alts eyns nit gekent geyn un koyfn.

00:11:12.363 --> 00:11:13.499
shoyn?

00:11:14.855 --> 00:11:16.081
kum, mayn zun.

00:11:17.555 --> 00:11:19.827
a dank. bald veln mir betn d-
